---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="COA Policy | PeptideResearch.eu">
  <section class="page-title bg-2">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
            <ul class="list-inline mb-0">
              <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="/" class="text-sm letter-spacing text-white text-uppercase font-weight-bold">Home</a></li>
              <li class="list-inline-item"><span class="text-white">|</span></li>
              <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="#" class="text-color text-uppercase text-sm letter-spacing">Policy</a></li>
            </ul>
             <h1 class="text-lg text-white mt-2">Certificate of Analysis (COA) Policy</h1>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
          <p class="lead mb-4">At PeptideResearch.eu, we believe in complete transparency regarding the quality of our reagents.</p>

          <h2 class="mt-4 mb-3">Batch-Specific Testing</h2>
          <p>Every batch of peptide we manufacture undergoes rigorous testing before it is released for sale. We do not rely on "generic" COAs. The COA you download corresponds to the current batch in stock.</p>

          <h2 class="mt-4 mb-3">Verification Methods</h2>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li class="mb-2"><i class="ti-check mr-2 text-color"></i><strong>HPLC (High-Performance Liquid Chromatography):</strong> Used to quantify purity and identify impurities.</li>
            <li class="mb-2"><i class="ti-check mr-2 text-color"></i><strong>MS (Mass Spectrometry):</strong> Used to confirm the molecular mass and identity of the peptide.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="mt-4 mb-3">Availability</h2>
          <p>Digital copies (PDF) of COAs are available for download directly from each product page. If you require a hard copy or raw data files for your records, please contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
